title: President hosts State luncheon in honour of Premier Li
content:
ISLAMABAD, Oct 15 (APP): President Asif Ali Zardari on Tuesday hosted State luncheon in the honour of Chinese Premier Li Qiang at Aiwan e Sadr.
Prime Minister Muhammad Shehbaz Sharif and Senate Chairman Syed Yousuf Raza Gilani attended the luncheon, President Secretariat Press Wing said in a press release.
Governors and Punjab Chief Minister Maryam Nawaz were also present.
Federal ministers, service chiefs, members of the parliament, diplomats, journalists and senior officials attended the luncheon.
